<i> Some people said to me</i>

00:02:18.404 --> 00:02:20.873
<i> "Why haven't you
 opened this cave up?"</i>

00:02:20.873 --> 00:02:24.443
<i>I hope you can begin to see,
how fragile this cave is.</i>

00:02:24.443 --> 00:02:25.678
<i> You do not want to do</i>

